==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Dern
<hw>Dern</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Dearn</er>,
<pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Hidden; concealed; secret.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Ye must be full <xex>dern</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Solitary; sad.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Dr.
H. More.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Derne</ent>⟦br⟧
